{
  "texts": [
    "Beyond Data and Architecture: Reasoning ModelsReasoning-optimized language models have recently emerged as a new pathway for improving capabilities.",
    "Over the past year, model developers have been increasing AI capability by optimizing models to \"think longer\".",
    "Ho and Berg [2025] estimates that the shift from conventional to reasoning models was equivalent to a 10× gain in pretraining compute.",
    "However, utilizing reasoning models is more costly due to the dramatically larger inference costs, which adds an additional dimension to measures of efficiency gains.",
    "Such improvements fall outside of our study's original 2012-2023 time period."
  ]
}